<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 12:25:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>基辅称乌克兰最高外交官本周将访华谈和</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-top-diplomat-visit-china-this-week-talk-peace-kyiv-says-2024-07-22/</link><description>乌克兰最高外交官将于周二应北京邀请访问中国，并举行会谈，基辅称会谈重点是如何结束俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争，以及中国在达成解决方案方面可能发挥的作用。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 11:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-top-diplomat-visit-china-this-week-talk-peace-kyiv-says-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>地缘政治再次打破市场步伐</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/geopolitics-is-back-break-markets-stride-2024-07-22/</link><description>政治因素已将全球市场从创纪录的峰值推倒，在动荡的几周内，随着投资者面临欧洲日益焦躁、美国孤立主义以及世界贸易脉搏放缓的前景，政治因素逐渐凸显出来。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 10:09:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/geopolitics-is-back-break-markets-stride-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾马科斯下令关闭离岸博彩业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-orders-closure-offshore-gaming-industry-2024-07-22/</link><description>总统小费迪南德·马科斯周一禁止在菲律宾设立的针对海外赌徒（包括中国大陆人）的赌博业务，因为与该行业有关的犯罪行为。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 10:07:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-orders-closure-offshore-gaming-industry-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦将在巴西 G20 金融会议上面临有关拜登竞选退出和特朗普的问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/yellen-face-questions-biden-campaign-exit-trump-g20-finance-meeting-brazil-2024-07-22/</link><description>在总统乔·拜登放弃连任竞选后，以及国际社会对唐纳德·特朗普可能重返白宫的担忧日益加剧，美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦本周面临二十国集团 (G20) 财长领导人关于美国政策承诺的质询。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 10:07:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/yellen-face-questions-biden-campaign-exit-trump-g20-finance-meeting-brazil-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：拜登退出，选举赌注发生变化，中国削减</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-07-22/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 10:02:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>跟随人民币贬值，被高估的印度卢比跌至历史新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/overvalued-indian-rupee-slips-record-low-tracking-chinese-yuan-declines-2024-07-22/</link><description>由于人民币贬值，印度卢比周一跌至历史低点，从某种角度来看，印度卢比的估值达到六年半以来最严重的水平。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 09:45:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/overvalued-indian-rupee-slips-record-low-tracking-chinese-yuan-declines-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>总统称菲律宾“不能让步”其南海立场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-cannot-yield-its-south-china-sea-position-president-says-2024-07-22/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周一表示，菲律宾在南海的立场“不能让步”、“不能动摇”，但将找到缓解争议海域紧张局势的方法。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 09:27:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-cannot-yield-its-south-china-sea-position-president-says-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>总统称菲律宾不能放弃南海立场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-still-assert-south-china-sea-rights-after-resupply-deal-with-2024-07-22/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周一表示，菲律宾在南海的立场上不能让步或动摇，但将找到方法缓和有争议水域的紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 07:52:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-still-assert-south-china-sea-rights-after-resupply-deal-with-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国允许延迟退休以应对人口问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-allow-delayed-retirement-combat-population-woes-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国将逐步提高法定退休年龄（目前是世界上最低的退休年龄之一），以允许人们工作更长时间，因为中国正在努力缓解养老金预算不断飙升的压力，许多省份已经面临赤字。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 07:51:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-allow-delayed-retirement-combat-population-woes-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国对其十年来的政策承诺的承诺面临越来越多的质疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-faces-growing-scepticism-over-its-commitment-decade-old-policy-pledges-2024-07-22/</link><description>随着中国经济失衡加剧，北京方面面临的压力越来越大，要求兑现其在上周领导层议程制定会议上重申的长达十年之久的政策承诺，但近年来未能取得重大突破。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 07:06:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-faces-growing-scepticism-over-its-commitment-decade-old-policy-pledges-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>西方矿商推动金属价格上涨以抵御中国竞争对手</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/western-miners-push-higher-metals-prices-ward-off-chinese-rivals-2024-07-22/</link><description>美国唯一的钴矿位于爱达荷州北部的森林中，是一片被封存的钢铁和泥土的休耕地，对于其所有者来说，运营成本太高，因为中国竞争对手已经向全球市场大量供应用于电动汽车电池和电子产品的蓝色金属。 。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 06:08:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/western-miners-push-higher-metals-prices-ward-off-chinese-rivals-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>雷诺首席执行官呼吁欧洲电动汽车过渡时间表保持灵活性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/renault-ceo-calls-flexibility-european-ev-transition-timeline-2024-07-22/</link><description>雷诺首席执行官卢卡·德梅奥(Luca De Meo)在周一向商业日报《回声报》发表的评论中对欧洲向电动汽车转型的时间表表示怀疑，并补充说，如果该汽车制造商想要实现其电动汽车目标，就必须降低成本。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 05:33:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/renault-ceo-calls-flexibility-european-ev-transition-timeline-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：拜登退出后华尔街情绪谨慎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-22/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 04:41:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：英伟达正在为中国市场准备新版旗舰人工智能芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-preparing-version-new-flaghip-ai-chip-chinese-market-sources-say-2024-07-22/</link><description>四位知情人士称，英伟达正在为中国市场开发一款新的旗舰人工智能芯片，该芯片将与美国当前的出口管制兼容。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 04:02:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-preparing-version-new-flaghip-ai-chip-chinese-market-sources-say-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国菲律宾大使馆要求回应针对新冠疫苗的宣传</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/chinas-philippines-embassy-demands-answers-propaganda-against-covid-vaccine-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国驻菲律宾大使馆周一表示，美国应尽快就其针对中国COVID-19疫苗的虚假宣传向菲律宾人民作出解释。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 02:37:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/chinas-philippines-embassy-demands-answers-propaganda-against-covid-vaccine-2024-07-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>